{"word":"ἀπωστός","slug":"ἀπωστός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀπωστός</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀπωθέω'><el>ἀπωθέω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>thrust</i> or <i>driven away from</i> a place, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>that can be driven away</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}